WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.412
This is GrekAI Skills for All, a free and open catalog of agent skills you can drop straight into Claude Code.

00:00:07.412 --> 00:00:15.187
Filter by category to find what you need. Everything here is a ready to use, self contained skill.

00:00:15.187 --> 00:00:23.537
Here is the Tutorial skill. It records narrated walkthroughs of your own app, exactly like the one you are watching now.

00:00:23.537 --> 00:00:29.949
Open any skill for its own page: what it does, when to use it, and the full README.

00:00:29.949 --> 00:00:39.124
Copy the one line install, and the skill lands in your Claude skills folder. Free to use, and open for your contributions.
